INCIPIT grimoire "cross_nested_mix_loops"

RITUALE main() REDDE REX
  EVOCA SERIES REX[3] arr
  VINCIRE arr[0] AD 1
  VINCIRE arr[1] AD 2
  VINCIRE arr[2] AD 3

  EVOCA REX outer AD 0
  EVOCA REX total AD 0

  DUM outer < 3
    VINCIRE outer AD outer + 1
    ITERUM v IN arr COM
      SI (outer == 2 ET v == 2) VEL (outer == 3 ET v == 1)
        RECEDE
      FIN SI
      SI outer == 3 ET v == 3
        FRANGE
      FIN SI
      VINCIRE total AD total + outer + v
    FIN ITERUM
  FIN DUM

  REDDE total
EXPLICIT RITUALE

EXPLICIT grimoire
